    <p>
        Now, when the
        <code>%command-update%</code> command is executed, the manager will check the specified packages and
        automatically update the files in your application.
    </p>
    <p>
        If files with the same names exist in different packages, for example, <code>custom.php</code>,
        then during their processing all keys from all files will be combined.
    </p>
